Name: Scythians
Code: scyth
Culture:
  - nomadic
Region:
  - asia
  - steppes
Emblem: session/portraits/emblems/scythians.png
History: The Scythians are a nomadic faction which can build its buildings
  anywhere on the map. Their buildings cost -50% resources and build time, but
  have -50% health and capture resistance. They have limited infantry, but a
  full roster of light and heavy cavalry. They have a raiding and looting bonus,
  and are excellent herders and hunters.
