CivBonuses:
  - Name: Nomadism
    History: The Scythians were a nomadic pastoral people.
    Description: Scythian structures have no territory bonus and are weak, but are
      very cheap and quick to build.
  - Name: Plunderers
    History: The Scythians sustained their economy through plunder.
    Description: Every enemy unit killed or building destroyed gives additional
      resources to the Scythian treasury.
