    Description: The nomadic tribal confederation of central Asia.
    Technologies:
      - Name: Falconry
        History: Falconry is a steppe tradition.
        Description: All Structures and Cavalry +25% vision range. Cavalry +25% meat
          gathering rate.
      - Name: Great Settlement
        History: The Scythians eventually conquered and settled cities along the Black
          Sea coast, founding powerful kingdoms on the Bosporus.
        Description: "Stone Walls and Fortresses are unlocked for the Scythians, and
          their structures can no longer pack and move, consequently gaining
          +50% health and +50% cost. "
      - Name: Parthian Tactics
        History: The Scythians practiced "Parthian Shot" tactics.
        Description: Ranged cavalry will automatically run away when enemies are near
